<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 21 at 12:34AM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Patchy Freezing Fog...
As clouds briefly clear associated with a departing weather
system, patchy freezing fog has developed. Localized reduction of
visibility to a half mile or less will be possible, especially
where a fresh snowpack overlaps with clear skies. Be prepared for
quickly changing visibility while driving.</description>
